A RESOLUTION
1 Commending Habitat for Humanity Georgia and its Georgia affiliates and recognizing March
2 5, 2025, as Habitat for Humanity Georgia Day at the state capitol; and for other purposes.
3 WHEREAS, Habitat for Humanity Georgia and its Georgia affiliates have been steadfast
4 advocates for affordable housing and community development, tirelessly working to provide
5 safe and decent housing for families in need; and
6 WHEREAS, Habitat for Humanity Georgia and its Georgia affiliates' efforts have
7 significantly contributed to the well-being and stability of countless communities across the
8 state; and
9 WHEREAS, on March 5, 2025, Habitat for Humanity Georgia and its Georgia affiliates will
10 undertake a significant advocacy initiative by framing a house on the Georgia State Capitol
11 grounds, symbolizing the importance of affordable housing and the need for continued
12 support and legislative action; and
13 WHEREAS, this event will bring together volunteers, community leaders, and legislators to
14 raise awareness and demonstrate the collective commitment to addressing housing challenges
15 in Georgia; and
